name: Super Kiwi 64
overview: Super Kiwi 64 is a 3D-Platformer and Collect-a-Thon, in a low poly late 90s console look. Features: - Low poly late 90s retro looks. - Kiwi can jump, glide, corkscrew-attack and stick to walls in order to jump up almost every wall. - The levels can be played in any order, and to reach the ending, it is not necessary to collect everything. - Eight compact open levels filled with tons of secrets. - Features a bird with a long beak!
